Enterprise 360 application 

This is the version 1.0 for Enterprise E360 application where user can ask Alexa below Items
1) How many role are there in our current system
2) What is planned for upcoming week
3) What is the favorite color
4) How many client issues are open 

We will add more features once , we get the good response
